QuestData.Title: A Strange Appetite
QuestData.Description: Food. I must have food.$B$BIn my time, the meat of the starfish brought not only strength, but also clarity of mind. This is what I must eat.$B$BBring this to me from the nearby shallows.$B$BWait much longer, and I will devour you instead.
QuestData.CompletionText: The juices of the starfish will clear my mind.
QuestData.RewardText: Yes, give it here! Well done, Wakener.
